  <brief_title>The Study of Blood Pressure Variability to Impact Arterial Stiffness and Carotid Atherosclerosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Relationship of Blood Pressure Variability, Arterial Stiffness and Carotid Atherosclerosis in Beijing Residents</official_title>
  <sponsors>
